    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>
      A simply arguments validation library with fluent API.
      
      Examples:
        Arg.NotNull(() => model);

        Arg.Validate(() => color)
          .NotNullOrWhitespace()
          .LengthLessOrEqualThan(20);

        Arg.Positive(releaseYear, nameof(releaseYear));
    </description>
    <summary>A simply arguments validation library with fluent API</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
        - Bug fix for IEnumerable type
        - The implementation was translated to use extension methods instead of the validator object
        - Improved performance
        - Increased test coverage
    </releaseNotes>
